Second Department,

June, 1966

(June 22, 1966) * In the Matter of Nathaniel Brewer, Petitioner, v. Supreme Court of the State of New York, Queens County, et al., Respondents.

Not published with other decisions of June, 1966, 26 A D 2d 545.— [Rep.

Proceeding pursuant to CPLR article 78 to prohibit respondents from proceeding to retry petitioner on any of the charges contained in indictment No. 646-1965. Application denied and proceeding dismissed, without costs. Ughetta, Acting P. J., Brennan, Hill, Rabin and Hopkins, JJ., concur.
